Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:48.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you draw these, Shippo?\NYou're very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:51.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, what a cute cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:53.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's you, Kagome.\NSee the resemblance?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:56.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And this is Inuyasha.\NAnd this one's Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:01:59.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the love triangle\nof a two-legged dog, a wolf...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and a cat who cried out,\N"I'm going home!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:05.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-wait a minute, Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:09.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you shown this\nembarrassing play to anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:11.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I showed Old Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:13.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She complimented me\nthat it was well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:17.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old Kaede... knows the reason\nwhy I fought with Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:20.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not only Old Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:22.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted everyone\nto praise me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so I showed them all\nin the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:25.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:30.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How embarrassing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:33.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess I can't go back\nto the village for a while.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:36.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not a lie! Kagome is my woman!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:39.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love Kagome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:42.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Wolf-Demon Tribe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I met Koga when we encountered\nthe Birds of Paradise...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:48.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}who tried to take the\NSacred Jewel fragments.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:50.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koga...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:52.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:55.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you love this guy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:59.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? Love?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:00.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love Inuyasha?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:04.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You must love him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:27.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, that side was all clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:30.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:40.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:43.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where?!\NWhere're the Birds of Paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:50.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you saying, Hakkaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:52.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Birds of Paradise are all dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You looked like such a fool just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:00.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up! That was a dirty trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:04.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only because you slacked off\nand fell asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:06.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:09.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're from the northern caverns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:18.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's someone in possession\nof a huge Sacred Jewel fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:21.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And he's the lord of some castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:23.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This isn't a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:26.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's combine forces,\nthe northern and western caverns...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and take the Sacred Jewel\nfrom the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:32.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll divvy up the fragments equally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, Koga? Wanna join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:39.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:43.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have something else\NI have to take care of first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:47.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see... well, we won't force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:49.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didja see? I think he's injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:57.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this, Koga?\NTurning them down?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:04:59.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we don't join them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:02.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the northern clan will get\nall the Sacred Jewel fragments!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let them go... it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:05.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:08.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not interested now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:12.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you want to go, I won't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:15.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're gonna join up\nwith the northern pack now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:20.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whoever wants\NSacred Jewel fragments, join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:22.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:28.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:46.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}First, I'll bite off that right arm!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:51.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never expected{\i0} it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:55.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that the demon bird would\nsteal my Sacred Jewel fragment...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:57.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}from my right arm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:00.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll get the fragment back in time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But before that comes that dog!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:13.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}With that huge sword,\nhe killed the demon bird in one swoop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:15.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That guy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:18.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't be satisfied until I kill him\nwith my own hands!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:24.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This wound isn't healing\nas fast as I hoped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:40.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This way, I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:42.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I get a sense of\NSacred Jewel fragments.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:46.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We really need Kagome, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:51.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's the only one who can sense\nthe Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:55.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, so Inuyasha,\ndon't fight with her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:56.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:57.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demon bear that\nterrorized the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:03.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's what the villagers said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:07.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At first, it was just\na mischievous bear ruining the fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:10.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suddenly, it grew huge\nand attacked the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:14.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha? You seem displeased.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:16.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:18.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure, it's important to search out\nthe Sacred Jewel fragments...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:19.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that Kagome senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:23.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But rather than a bear,\NI'm searching for a wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koga...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:28.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We know that\nthat skinny wolf-demon Koga...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:32.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,still has two\NSacred Jewel fragments in his legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:36.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If this mountain smelled\nmore like wolf than bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:38.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd feel more like fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:40.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you want to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that butchering Koga\ncomes first with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:45.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga, his love rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:55.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, you don't bug Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:56.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and you won't feel his fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:03.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:05.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NThey're ordinary mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:08.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ordinary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:10.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're pretty cocky, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:13.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,From the looks of you,\nyou have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:16.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then,\nyou can leave the women.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:20.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you...\NI'll give you a good piece of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you don't want to get hurt,\nbetter run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:25.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:27.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! I can feel\nthe Sacred Jewel coming closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:31.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's in his forehead!\NThe Sacred Jewel fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:02.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! What a huge bugger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:06.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But your head is still just a bear, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:18.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's poison insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:20.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're taking\nthe Sacred Jewel fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:46.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:48.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:50.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fine with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:53.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This time, Naraku won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:22.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dear, dear... you've set your sights\nquite high this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:26.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it's easier for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel fragment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It makes demons even stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:41.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,an enticing opiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You plan to lure them here with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:52.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't beat them\nwithout this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're either careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:10:58.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,or cowardly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:02.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but you love traps, don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:04.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,my dear master?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:11.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here it is... the castle full\nof Sacred Jewel fragments.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When the men of the castle appear,\nnever mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:15.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:16.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:18.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They don't even have guards posted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:24.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:26.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go! Get 'im.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Only small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:54.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:58.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone more virile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:35.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:42.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:43.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:46.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- He went with the northern pack!\N- Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:48.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:51.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I got just one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a Sacred Jewel fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:59.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry to the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:02.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you don't, everyone will be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:12.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A Jewel fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:14.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm using it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:20.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's rest inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How did you make it back here\nwith those injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:33.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:55.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:05.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wolves...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:08.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could they be wolf-demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:11.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But why would they be here\nin this castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:46.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that? They're still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:54.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't sense any life in these men.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:14.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You see? Even if they're put down,\nthey revive immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:16.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're supposed to be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How come\nthey keep coming back alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:23.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't cut them\nnor can you beat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:26.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if you lop off their heads,\nthey'll reattach right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:29.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is my Death Corpse Dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:32.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh? Here already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:36.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted to play a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:39.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:03.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:07.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're all collapsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's Koga\nof the Wolf-Demon Tribe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:32.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koga?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:37.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!\NHow could you be so cruel!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me tell you one thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:44.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I got here,\nyour comrades had all been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:46.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up!\NYou're covered head to toe in blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:48.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't lie to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:51.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! It was a trap!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:53.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:57.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We came here looking for\nsomeone named Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:57.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:16:59.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:01.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When we got here,\nall the wolf-demons were lying here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:03.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but then they all came alive and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:06.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!\NDon't try to protect such a guy! You cur!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:13.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dead when you got here? That's bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:14.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:18.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We were trapped! It's Naraku's trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:21.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We followed Naraku's poison insects\nto this castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:25.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The wolf-demons probably followed\nsome clues here, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:26.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,then were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:29.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Koga arrives to\nsave his comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:34.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only to find Inuyasha\ncovered in their blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:38.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The wrath of having his comrades killed\nwon't be quelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:40.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They will fight to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:44.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The blood has gone to Koga's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:48.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As it is,\nthey really {\i1}will{\i0} fight to the death!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:51.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to stop them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...but how?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:18.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must stop them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:20.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but...but how?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:25.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}His arm's gotten stronger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:47.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga! You found another\NJewel fragment for your arm!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:53.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You stole my fragment\nthe last time we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:57.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This one's even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:05.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That glow!\NIt's not the light from the Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:09.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's black and the glow is warped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:12.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that fragment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:28.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop, Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:30.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:32.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:35.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The one who killed\nyour friends is not Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:41.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I only believe what I see\nwith my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:42.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:44.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:49.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This hard-headed punk\ncan't understand complicated things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:54.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fools like him can only be tamed\nwith brute strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:58.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Wolf-Demon Tribe lives in packs\nand cherish their comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Seeing so many killed at one time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:02.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga's wrath won't be easily controlled!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:07.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought he'd listen to you\nat least, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:11.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't blame Inuyasha...\nsince Koga is attacking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:13.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no choice\nbut to stop him with a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:16.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku is trying to make me fight Koga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:20.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he's watching us from somewhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:25.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inside the mansion?\NI can smell Naraku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:27.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:32.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you looking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll we do? Shall we help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:40.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha was looking for Naraku,\nthe one who laid the trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:43.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then is he... inside the mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:47.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Charging into the enemy's trap\nis not a smart strategy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:51.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we have no choice do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:14.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?\NWhat're you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:18.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:21.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:25.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's Sango...\nand you're Miroku, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:27.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's agent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:29.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell us! Where is Naraku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:34.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But he left something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:38.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He says this should keep you busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:43.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demon puppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:47.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then...\NI'll go see what's going on outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:49.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga and Inuyasha, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:54.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not my types at all...\nso I don't care which one dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.59,0:23:51.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga and Inuyasha\nhave begun their duel to the death!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.49,0:23:54.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's goal\nis the Sacred Jewel fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.80,0:23:56.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To get the fragments\nin Koga's legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.40,0:23:57.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,rather than dirty his hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.66,0:23:59.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku is trying to use Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.03,0:24:03.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Tetsusaiga has been repelled!\NInuyasha's right arm is broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.90,0:24:05.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha faces\none crisis after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.97,0:24:09.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but he will {\i1}not{\i0} lose\nto some female demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.14,0:24:10.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.64,0:24:12.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"The Deadly Trap of Kagura,\nthe Wind Sorceress!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.01,0:24:13.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
